{"tid":1610683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開始睇唔到希望...","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T19:26:37.000Z","uid":37240,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cedf16ef569b4c987f7600c6389e5ffc909c4ba3","tid":1610683,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"班高官繼續潛水<br />\n繼續享受榮華富貴<br />\n無視訴求，一味武力鎮壓<br />\n呢個殺人政權加上殺人軍隊<br />\n做咁多野都未爭取到5大訴求<br />\n成個香港都出左問題<br />\n<br />\n如果可以既話，我希望有革命組織推倒港共政府重新黎過<br />\n每一次想放棄既時候都幻想美好既香港會係點<br />\n香港應該好似瑞士咁始終保持中立，每個係香港既人都有完善保障同自由<br />\n但係而家港共明刀明槍急劇中共化<br />\n好似只會變成第二個新疆<br />\n<br />\n明明香港一直幫中共搵錢<br />\n到底點解中共仲要逼死香港？<br />\n純粹開始攰想呻下<br />\n香港人還拖！點都要得到五大訴求，有真普選<br />\n再重組警隊，將政府變為做香港政府而唔係中國香港市政府！<br />\n唔可以放棄..."},{"pid":"758b4748ac6ed10f45dcabd0239c5af6d3734fc6","tid":1610683,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:04:34.000Z","msg":"專心攬炒啦<br />\n過唔到炒到一半共產黨會識止損呢"},{"pid":"a93f602c5db680de036b090ee1d60029f9bcc50a","tid":1610683,"uid":303614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:05:17.000Z","msg":"我睇劉細良啲分析，其實我地係絕處有生機。<br />\n大意如下： see link &gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有無人覺得再無希望<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aiFBMjV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aiFBMjV</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ced2578b17cb085ec8e5cb37ed79583268cd5719","tid":1610683,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9MfLYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9MfLYk.jpg&h=06a4ed67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce04c3efbfb774e0a87af41745cfb42bf46389b9","tid":1610683,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/10/01/world/01china-live-carrie/merlin_161882685_7604aea3-a92e-4e6e-9933-f322607f4592-superJumbo.jpg?quality=90